- cs.FL (Formal Languages and Automata Theory) is a possibility as the paper deals with the interpretation of formulas in a topological vector space.
- cs.GR (Graphics) is a less likely category, but still a possibility as the paper mentions a Taylor expansion decomposition in the quantitative model of Intuitionist Differential Linear Logic.
